up... What's the real reason?

45
00:02:49,036 --> 00:02:51,770
You were always suspicious.

46
00:02:53,090 --> 00:02:55,958
And you were
always a narcissist.

47
00:02:56,026 --> 00:02:58,726
I was hoping that time

48
00:02:58,796 --> 00:03:01,897
and maturity would open
the doors for us starting over.

49
00:03:03,684 --> 00:03:05,783
Dada! Dada!

50
00:03:05,853 --> 00:03:08,320
Clearly, you don't
know me very well.

51
