patients... Including Lily.

132
00:06:49,993 --> 00:06:51,626
Look, Nic,

133
00:06:51,695 --> 00:06:54,729
Lane is the most respected
oncologist in Georgia,

134
00:06:54,798 --> 00:06:57,398
not to mention someone
whose work I have admired

135
00:06:57,467 --> 00:06:59,133
and studied since med school.

136
00:06:59,202 --> 00:07:00,735
Look, I have pulled every ounce

137
00:07:00,804 --> 00:07:02,854
of research that I
can possibly find

138
00:07:02,923 --> 00:07:04,217
