intensification programs

139
00:07:04,241 --> 00:07:06,374
both here and
abroad... Look at this.

140
00:07:06,443 --> 00:07:08,827
These are from Lane's clinic.

141
00:07:08,895 --> 00:07:10,907
Her chemo protocols
are significantly higher

142
00:07:10,931 --> 00:07:13,632
than even the most
aggressive programs.

143
00:07:17,504 --> 00:07:20,088
Did you tell Conrad?

144
00:07:20,156 --> 00:07:21,956
I tried.

145
00:07:22,025 --> 00:07:24,726
But if I'm gonna accuse his
mentor of something so awful,

146
00:07:24,795 --> 00:07:26,761
I need more proof.

147
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:28,663
Nic...

148
00:07:28,732 --> 00:07:31,432
do you think, maybe,

149
00:07:31,501 --> 00:07:35,970
you are letting your
personal feelings for Lane

150
00:07:36,039 --> 00:07:38,439
cloud your judgment?

151
00:07:40,627 --> 00:07:43,311
It's no secret that you
two don't get along.

152
00:07:44,447 --> 00:07:45,447
No.

153
00:07:45,515 --> 00:07:47,115
I'm doing my job...

154
00:07:47,183 --> 00:07:49,651
A job that Lane threatened,
by the way... so you

155
00:07:49,719 --> 00:07:51,253
just keep an eye on Lily.

156
00:07:51,321 --> 00:07:53,621
You're her doctor...
That's<i> your</i> job.

157
00:08:03,316 --> 00:08:07,052
Do you know how much longer
Doc Davenport is gonna be?

158
00:08:07,104 --> 00:08:09,048
I really need to get
back to rehearsal.

159
00:08:09,072 --> 00:08:11,005
Nigel, I'm Dr. Hawkins.

160
00:08:11,074 --> 00:08:13,207
Dr. Davenport
asked me to stop by.

161
00:08:15,328 --> 00:08:16,444
Look, let me save you

162
00:08:16,513 --> 00:08:19,296
