unnecessary road.

163
00:08:19,366 --> 00:08:21,461
Yes, I'm showing signs
of severe malnourishment,

164
00:08:21,485 --> 00:08:23,345
and no, I don't have
an eating disorder.

165
00:08:23,369 --> 00:08:25,937
I suffer from chronic
digestive pain,

166
00:08:26,006 --> 00:08:28,372
and it makes it almost
impossible to eat.

167
00:08:28,441 --> 00:08:31,109
It's been over a decade,
and no, none of my doctors

168
00:08:31,178 --> 00:08:33,695
back in New York
seem to know what it is.

169
00:08:33,763 --> 00:08:36,481
So before you ask,
the answer is no.

170
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:39,150
No more tests. Zero.

171
00:08:39,219 --> 00:08:41,497
I've been poked and prodded
by every doctor imaginable.

172
00:08:41,521 --> 00:08:43,699
The only doctor I haven't
seen is a gynecologist.

173
00:08:43,723 --> 00:08:45,139
Eh, they're overrated.

174
00:08:47,127 --> 00:08:49,460
I've accepted I'm just
gonna live with this pain

175
00:08:49,529 --> 00:08:51,262
for the rest of my life.

176
00:08:51,315 --> 00:08:53,293
I'm a ballet dancer...
I'm used to intense pain.

177
00:08:53,317 --> 00:08:56,101
- That's no way to live, man.
- I've made my peace.

178
00:08:56,153 --> 00:08:58,436
Only thing that matters
now is my career.

179
00:08:58,505 --> 00:09:00,771
So can I just get some
steroids for my ankle,

180
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,957
- so I can get back to my show?
- Look...

181
00:09:03,043 --> 00:09:04,342
I get it.

182
00:09:04,411 --> 00:09:07,478
I get how important your
career is to you, okay?

183
00:09:07,548 --> 00:09:10,764
If you leave, you'll be right
back with another injury.

184
00:09:10,833 --> 00:09:13,334
Maybe a day, a
week, or even a month,

185
00:09:13,403 --> 00:09:15,303
but it will happen.

186
00:09:15,389 --> 00:09:16,799
Your twisted ankle's
just the beginning.

187
00:09:16,823 --> 00:09:18,784
You're malnourished,
and your body can't handle

188
00:09:18,808 --> 00:09:20,786
the stress of being a
professional dancer anymore.

189
00:09:20,810 --> 00:09:23,310
- So I should just give up?
- Give me 24 hours, and let me

190
00:09:23,379 --> 00:09:25,357
see if I can figure out
what's wrong with you.

191
00:09:25,381 --> 00:09:27,465
It's worth it if I can
save your career.

192
00:09:27,534 --> 00:09:29,267
Right?

193
00:09:38,579 --> 00:09:40,295
You found me.

194
00:09:40,364 --> 00:09:41,841
- Wasn't lookin' for you.
- Ouch.

195
