00:22:22,992 --> 00:22:25,136
her clinic, and they've
already done a full panel on Lily.

500
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:27,328
Isabel,<i> you've</i> worked
here long enough to know

501
00:22:27,396 --> 00:22:28,963
